/span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">clists, but I recognise that this is not the case in other parts of the country.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">My s</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">uggestions for improvements are</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:OpenSymbol; font-size:12pt">•</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">strict liability</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:OpenSymbol; font-size:12pt">•</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">an education campaign aimed at drivers and cyclists</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:OpenSymbol; font-size:12pt">•</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">an ongoing, high-profile campaign by the police, targeting dangerou</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">s, aggressive and distracted drivers in particular aimed at improving the overall standard of driving on our roads and reducing the level of casual law-breaking by motorists (speeding, hand-held mobiles etc.)</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:OpenSymbol; font-size:12pt">•</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">segregated</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> facilities will in the longer term e</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">ncourage more cyclists to take to the roads.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">December 2013</span><a name="_GoBack"></a></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Segoe Print'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>